	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a few questions about screen resolutions.
<br />
<br />1) Why is standard resolution sometimes called 480i when there are 448 visible lines?
<br />
<br />2) How many pixels do HDTV's sample from an NTSC (or PAL) signal per line.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
