	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So the real resolution is exactly 35/32 times the amount of visible pixels?
<br />
<br />256 onscreen pixels:
<br />32 8x8 cells
<br />280 pixels
<br />3.58 Mhz * 3 / 2
<br />dithered artifact: 6 pixel long rainbow
<br />
<br />320 onscreen pixels:
<br />40 8x8 cells
<br />350 pixels
<br />3.58 Mhz * 15 / 8
<br />dithered artifact: 30 pixel long ranibow 
<br />
<br />336 (341.67) onscreen pixels:
<br />42 8x8 cells
<br />373.33 pixels
<br />3.58 * 2
<br />dithered artifact: solid color
<br />
<br />384 onscreen pixels:
<br />48 8x8 cells
<br />460 pixels
<br />3.58 * 9 / 4
<br />dithered artifact: 18 pixel long rainbow

		

		</td>
	</tr>
